title: The Saints - I'm Stranded (full album 2007 version) FLAC
description: 2007 digitally remastered and expanded reissue of the Australian Punk band's 1977 debut album now featuring an additional eight bonus tracks featuring outtakes, B-sides and all four tracks from their One Two Three Four EP.. Never purposely fashionable, The Saints were Garage rockers caught up in the Punk scene, but their raw dirty sound fit perfectly into the Punk aesthetic.. This release is coinciding with a monumental occasion in Aussie musical history: The three surviving members of The Saints (Chris Bailey, Ed Kuepper and Ivor Hay) are reuniting for a one-off historical performance in Brisbane in July of 2007. 18 tracks. EMI
